
# 👶 Baby Detection, Tracking & Alert System (YOLOv5 + YouTube Integration)

<p align="center">
  <img src="docs/banner.jpg" alt="Baby Detection Banner" width="700">
</p>

---

## 📌 Overview

This project uses **YOLOv5** to detect, track, and alert when a baby moves outside a **predefined safety zone**.
It supports:

* 🎥 **Real-time webcam monitoring**
* 📂 **Custom/local videos**
* 📺 **YouTube videos**

**Goal**: Create a smart monitoring system for nurseries or research projects.

---

## 🚀 Features

* ✅ **Baby Detection** — Trained YOLOv5 model to detect babies in frames.
* ✅ **Tracking** — Continuous tracking with bounding boxes.
* ✅ **Safety Zone** — Virtual zone to ensure the baby stays safe.
* ✅ **Alert System** — Visual warnings for unsafe positions.
* ✅ **YouTube Integration** — Process videos directly from YouTube links.
* ✅ **Colab-Friendly** — Runs without local GPU.

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

| Tool/Library | Purpose                   |
| ------------ | ------------------------- |
| **Python 3** | Main programming language |
| **YOLOv5**   | Object detection          |
| **PyTorch**  | Deep learning framework   |
| **OpenCV**   | Video & image processing  |
| **yt-dlp**   | YouTube video downloading |
| **Pygame**   | Sound alerts (local runs) |

---

## 📂 Dataset

* **Source**: Custom dataset via [Roboflow](https://roboflow.com)
* **Size**: 2,000+ annotated baby images
* **Format**: YOLO TXT labels
* **Classes**:

```
0 baby
```

Example Training Images:

<p align="center">
  <img src="docs/sample_training.jpg" alt="Training Example" width="500">
</p>

