## ⚙️ Setup & Usage (Google Colab)

### 1️⃣ Clone YOLOv5

```bash
!git clone https://github.com/ultralytics/yolov5
%cd yolov5
!pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 2️⃣ Download Dataset

```bash
curl -L "YOUR_ROBOFLOW_DATASET_LINK" > roboflow.zip
unzip roboflow.zip
```

### 3️⃣ Train Model

```bash
!python train.py --img 640 --batch 16 --epochs 50 --data data.yaml --weights yolov5s.pt
```

### 4️⃣ Download YouTube Video

```python
from yt_dlp import YoutubeDL
video_url = "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EISMLMybScA&t=4s"
ydl_opts = {"format": "best[ext=mp4]", "outtmpl": "/content/baby_video.mp4"}
with YoutubeDL(ydl_opts) as ydl:
    ydl.download([video_url])
```

### 5️⃣ Run Detection + Alert

```bash
python detect_and_alert.py --weights runs/train/exp/weights/best.pt --source baby_video.mp4
```

---

## 📊 Detection Box Colors

| Color           | Meaning                          |
| --------------- | -------------------------------- |
| 🟦 **Blue Box** | Baby inside safety zone          |
| 🟥 **Red Box**  | Baby outside safety zone (alert) |

